room_title: Escape room "The Show Must Go On" by Hour Escape Port Jeff in New York
room_description: You’ve been recruited by a Private Investigator to help find the missing actress! Travel in time and space to the dressing room of famous 1950’s Hollywood actress, Veronica Lakes. Her show is set to start in an hour, but we believe she has been kidnapped. We need your help finding her and to figure out who the kidnapper is. Will you solve the mystery? Time is running out!
